.SH NAME
.PP
bup\-meta \- create or extract a metadata archive
.SH SYNOPSIS
.TP
.B bup meta \-\-create
[\-R] [\-v] [\-q] [\-\-no\-symlinks] [\-\-no\-paths] [\-f \f[I]file\f[]]
<\f[I]paths\f[]\&...>
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B bup meta \-\-list
[\-v] [\-q] [\-f \f[I]file\f[]]
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B bup meta \-\-extract
[\-v] [\-q] [\-\-numeric\-ids] [\-\-no\-symlinks] [\-f \f[I]file\f[]]
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B bup meta \-\-start\-extract
[\-v] [\-q] [\-\-numeric\-ids] [\-\-no\-symlinks] [\-f \f[I]file\f[]]
.RS
